    <h2>Collecting and Using Your Personal Data</h2>
    <h3>Types of Data Collected</h3>
    <h4>Personal Data</h4>
    <p>While using Our Service, We may ask You to provide Us with certain personally identifiable information such as:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Email address</li>
        <li>First and last name</li>
        <li>Phone number (optional)</li>
        <li>Country (optional)</li>
        <li>Age (optional)</li>
    </ul>

    <h4>Usage Data</h4>
    <p>Collected automatically and may include:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Device IP address, browser type/version, pages visited, date/time of visit, device identifiers, and diagnostic data.</li>
        <li>Mobile device type, operating system, and Internet browser type when accessing via mobile.</li>
    </ul>

    <h4>Information from Third-Party Social Media Services</h4>
    <p>You may log in via Google or other third-party accounts. If so, We may collect Personal Data already associated with that account (name, email, etc.).</p>

