    <h2>User-Generated Content (UGC)</h2>
    <p>The Application allows Users to post notes You are solely responsible for the content You upload. Prohibited content includes, but is not limited to: sexually explicit, violent, hateful, misleading, or copyrighted material. The Company reserves the right to remove any content that violates these rules or suspend accounts that misuse the Service. The Application provides a reporting feature so Users can report inappropriate content. Reported content may be reviewed and removed by our moderation team.</p>

    <hr>

    <h2>Firebase Services</h2>
    <p>We use Firebase services (including Authentication, Firestore Database, Cloud Messaging, and Analytics). Firebase may collect data such as: Device identifiers, crash logs, IP address, and usage data. This information is used to provide, secure, and improve the Application.</p>

    <hr>

    <h2>Push Notifications</h2>
    <p>We use Firebase Cloud Messaging (FCM) to send push notifications (such as chat messages, updates, and alerts). You can disable notifications at any time through your device settings.</p>

